data.description: Peaceful country living awaits in this quaint mobile home on over 16 acres in Ludowici. Step inside to find a large living room that opens up to the spacious kitchen & separate dining area. The master bedroom features two closets as well as an ensuite bathroom with a soaking tub & walk-in shower. With three more sizeable bedrooms, there is sure to be plenty of space for your family to enjoy. Enjoy all the perks of country living on this vast property including an outdoor shed, pond for fishing, creek and a private driveway.  Property includes 3 lots in Long County and 1 adjacent lot in Liberty County. See arial maps parcels identified.
